description: It comes after thousands of images of Irish women were shared online causing "upset and anger".
title: Laws proposed after intimate images of Irish women shared without consent
title_page: Laws proposed after intimate images of Irish women shared without consent - BBC News
maintext: "I would like to send a clear message to anyone whose images have been shared without your consent: It is not your fault, you didn't do anything wrong, and you're not to blame," she said.
